            "id": 6010855,
            "title": "2家銀行型金控獲利搶先看！玉山前5月續創新高 永豐賺逾百億",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近月<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/usdtwd\">新台幣</a>兌美元匯率強勢走升，壽險公司遭遇匯損危機，但 2 家銀行型金控玉山及永豐營運相對持穩，今 (6) 日搶先公布 5 月自結，玉山金單月獲利亮麗，前 5 月大賺 141 億元，改寫史上同期新高紀錄，永豐金單月受認列未分配盈餘稅影響，較上月下滑，但前 5 月獲利已突破百億大關，證券子公司受惠股市反彈獲利回神。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010855%2Fl%2Fda57817c53d926a9751045351d1a54d5.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">2家銀行型金控獲利搶先看！玉山前5月續創新高 永豐賺逾百億。(圖:shutterstock)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>玉山金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2884:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2884\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2884-TW</a>) 公布 2025 年 5 月自結獲利，單月稅後純益 28.5 億元，月增 13.54%、年增 13.9%；累計前 5 月稅後純益 141.5 億元，續創歷年同期新高，較去年同期增加 34.73%，每股稅後純益 (EPS) 為 0.88 元。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要子公司玉山銀行，5 月稅後純益 28.33 億元，累計稅後純益 142.6 億元，較去年同期增加 47.84%；玉山證券單月稅後純益 1.46 億元，累計稅後純益 7 億元；玉山創投單月稅後純益 0.57 億元，累計稅後虧損收斂至 1.2 億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>永豐金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2890:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2890\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2890-TW</a>)2025 年 5 月自結稅後純益 13.31 億元，較上月減少 27.1%，主要因認列未分配盈餘稅 3.9 億元 (去年為 6 月認列)，累計前 5 月稅後純益 103.58 億元，年減 0.7%，每股稅後純益 (EPS)0.82 元，年化 ROE 12.28%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>子公司單月表現方面，永豐銀行 5 月稅後純益 14.47 億元，月減 21.4%，獲利減少主要因金融交易收益月減所致。永豐金證券 5 月稅後純益 2.53 億元，較上月大增 2.47 億元，主要受惠於 5 月台股日均量回溫，帶動手續費收入動能提升及承銷部位評價回升。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>子公司累計獲利方面，永豐銀行稅後純益 94.92 億元，年增 19.5%，續創歷年同期新高，主要受惠於利息淨收益與手續費淨收益皆有雙位數的成長。 其中，個體利息淨收益年增 28.9%、手續費淨收益年增 23.9%，金融交易相關收益年減 29%。永豐金證券前 5 月稅後純益 14.61 億元，年減 34.3%，主要受到台股日均量相較於去年同期回落且行情波動劇烈，手續費淨收益與資本利得皆減少所致。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>此外，國票金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2889:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2889\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2889-TW</a>) 同步公告 5 月自結稅後純益為 1 億 5303 萬元，較上月轉虧為盈，累計前 5 月稅後純益為 3 億 5229 萬元，較去年同期減少 59.21%，每股稅後純益 (EPS) 0.1 元，5 月底每股淨值 11.71 元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
